Introduction

The KingDom (Korean: 더킹덤; Japanese: キングダム) (formerly known as KINGDOM (킹덤) is a seven-member boy group under GF Entertainment. The group consists of Dann, Arthur, Mujin, Louis, Ivan, Jahan, and Hwon. Each member represents a different king with their own fantasy Kingdoms. They debuted on February 18, 2021, with their first mini album History of Kingdom : Part 1. Arthur

On May 25, 2022, GF Entertainment announced Chiwoo's departure and said that the group would continue to promote as a six-member group.

On August 31, 2022, Hwon was introduced as the newest member of the group.

On January 17, 2025 GF Entertainment announced that Hwon has left the group due to personal reasons.
